title: RECAP: Tech drops close games against Missouri, UCLA - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: RECAP: Tech drops close games against Missouri, UCLA - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: CATHEDRAL CITY, Calif. – Texas Tech softball (4-9) dropped a pair of one-run contests to No. 16 Missouri (10-3) and No. 6 UCLA (9-3) Friday night at the Mary Nutter Collegiate Classic.
